---
title: Pinoy-Style Chicken Breast Adobo with Garlic Rice
description: Don't confuse this national dish of the Philippines with its Mexican counterpart. This version relies on soy sauce, vinegar and lots of onions, garlic and cracked pepper to make the dish come alive! Here's what's to come: savoury garlic rice plated beside sautéed bok choy and cabbage, then topped with pan-seared chicken that is finished in a delectable onion sauce.
